# Plantyst Portal API (moved to apidocs.plantyst.com)

<link rel="canonical" href="https://apidocs.plantyst.com/" />

## This documentation has permanently moved to [https://apidocs.plantyst.com](https://apidocs.plantyst.com/)

The Plantyst Portal API documentation is now maintained in the OpenAPI format and published at the new address:

**[https://apidocs.plantyst.com/](https://apidocs.plantyst.com/)**

This Apiary page is **no longer maintained** and will be shut down together with the Apiary service. Please update your bookmarks and links to https://apidocs.plantyst.com/.

The API itself is unchanged and keeps running at `https://portal.plantyst.com/api/` - only the documentation has a new home. The new documentation is a complete, up-to-date rewrite: it covers all current endpoints, request/response examples verified against production, webhooks and SCIM provisioning.

---

